nodes.text: Miharr was a female Cathar of the Bounty Supply Company stationed on the reconstituted Sith Empire's Vaiken Spacedock during the Cold War and Galactic War between the Empire and the Galactic Republic.
Miharr appears in BioWare's 2011 massively multiplayer online role-playing video game Star Wars: The Old Republic as the Bounty Supply reputation vendor.
